席，唔好投錯！<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">傳統泛民</span> + <span class=\"teal\">國際線</span> + <span class=\"maroon\">本土</span> (3席)<br />\nDQ者自有Plan B<br />\n<em><ins>排第四、五<span class=\"red\">不是</span>取代Plan B的理由</ins></em></span></strong>"}]}